      "message": "You need to add the `LogPresenceChange` property to `required` array here as well\notherwise configurations are not required to provide the property.\n\nIf there are configurations without the property then EM will not expose it on D-Bus and create the interface with a different set of properties, which is not allowed in D-Bus.\n\nIt will also cause errors and exceptions in PDI clients trying to read the missing property.",
